item.title: I downloaded a source but i'm still using hybridscape?
item.dc:creator: @93dcthugs93 93dcthugs93
item.description:
@93dcthugs93 wrote:

Go into newscape click compileserver.bat finish that click runserver.bat minimize that fill in the port and use the IP 0.0.0.0 just to check out your server.

To host it you need Hamachi, give people the port & your hamachi IP. They can connect now.
